Interface ClassMapper

public interface ClassMapper

        Parameters:
        id - the Id of the element

      • allInstancesOf

        @Nonnull
Stream<Id> allInstancesOf(ClassBean metaClass,
                                    boolean strict)
        Retrieves all instances of the given metaClass.
        Parameters:
        metaClass - the meta-class to compute the instances of
        strict - true if the lookup searches for strict instances
        Returns:
        an Stream containing the instances of the metaClass
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if any parameter is null
        UnsupportedOperationException - if the mapper doesn't support the lookup of all instances
